high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the knife to the right of the tomato.
Turn to your right and walk to the sink.
Cut up the the apple in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave in the corner of the room.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn to your right and walk back to the sink.
Pick up one piece of the apple your cut up earlier.
Turn around and walk back to the microwave.
Place the piece of apple inside the microwave, heat it up and then pick it back up.
Walk to the trash can to the left of the microwave.
Put the apple piece in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of apple into the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, go straight and to the right to the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into pieces.
Turn around, go straight and to the right to the microwave at the end of the counter.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn right, straight and to the right to the sink.
Take a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn around, go straight and to the right to the microwave at the end of the counter.
Cook the apple in the microwave, take the apple from the microwave.
Go to the bin to the left of the microwave
Put the apple into the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple into a bin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter.
Take the knife on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Slice the apple in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Open the door on the microwave and place the knife inside then close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Take an apple slice in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the microwave.
Place the apple slice inside, close the door, and turn it on. Then open the door and remove the slice.
Turn left and walk to the trash can.
Put the apple slice in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a microwaved apple slice.
